                    Licensed under <a href="https://github.com/DouglasCAyers/sfdc-convert-attachments-to-chatter-files/blob/master/LICENSE" target="_blank">BSD-3 License</a>.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

</apex:page>